ps://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-053.jpg?height=427&width=401&top__y=980&top__x=468","line":1060,"embedded":true},{"title":"|764x188","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-055.jpg?height=256&width=1043&top__y=1369&top__x=362","line":1091,"embedded":true},{"title":"0, \\frac{\\sqrt{5}}{5}\\.$ )；\n(4) $\\triangle F M N$ 周长的最小值为 $\\sqrt{2}+1$.\n\n其中正确结论的为（）\nA. (1)(2)\nB. (2)(3)\nC. (3)(4)\nD. (1)(4)\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-078.jpg?height=427&width=404&top__y=980&top__x=466","line":1534},{"title":"2,+\\infty)$\nD. $(-\\infty, 2) \\cup(2,+\\infty)$\n\n#### 10.2.2 【 练 1-1\n\n圆 $x^{2}+y^{2}+4 \\sin \\theta \\cdot x+4 \\cos \\theta \\cdot y+1=0$ 的半径等于 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.3 【 练 1-2\n\n已知 $A(-2,2) ， B(2,6)$ ，则以 $A B$ 为直径的圆的标准方程为 $\\qquad$ .\n\n#### 10.2.4 【 练 1-3\n\n正方形草地 $A B C D$ 边长 $1.2 ， E$ 到 $A B ， A D$ 距离为 $0.2 ， F$ 到 $B C ， C D$ 距离为 0.4 ，有个圆形通道经过 $E ， F$ ，且与 $A D$ 只有一个交点，求圆形通道的周长 $\\qquad$ . (精确到 $0.01)$\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-118.jpg?height=318&width=304&top__y=889&top__x=299","line":2226},{"title":"                                                             | 201x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=201&top__y=1293&top__x=738","line":2683,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 212x197","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=197&width=212&top__y=1513&top__x=723","line":2684,"embedded":true},{"title":"                                                             | 201x156","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-144.jpg?height=156&width=201&top__y=1742&top__x=738","line":2685,"embedded":true},{"title":"|401x429","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-161.jpg?height=429&width=401&top__y=982&top__x=468","line":3034,"embedded":true},{"title":"50,60$ ) 内的人数为 16 ，则下列结论正确的是（）\n![","target":"https://cdn.mathpix.com/cropped/2024_11_11_d544063a66ff94b9c61bg-185.jpg?height=435&width=618&top__y=1781&top__x=296","line":3503}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1c51oxn","at":1771213610659}},"smart_blocks:00-知识汇总/09-讲义汇总/XDF讲义/FY25 高三数学秋季【行远班教材】修改版本.md#": {"path":null,"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.09005282,-0.02210007,0.05083299,0.01253472,0.03095851,-0.01500811,-0.05098961,0.01612245,0.03880079,0.06726521,0.03500084,-0.06825641,0.05376306,-0.00111226,0.00536862,0.00086646,0.00236398,-0.04882766,-0.05929325,-0.01603318,0.11969707,-0.00887843,-0.02992988,-0.05892531,0.05134538,0.04747059,-0.01820272,-0.06266166,-0.04382852,-0.18104596,-0.02794211,0.07859194,0.05491842,0.03246256,0.04384226,-0.05976173,-0.03434689,0.06272999,0.00616815,0.05268471,-0.01827577,0.0781218,-0.00247192,-0.01187347,-0.02345622,-0.10297305,-0.03986634,0.00577062,0.03076928,-0.01680347,-0.02504876,-0.03675055,0.00253555,0.0497816,-0.01031892,0.00341619,0.03611497,0.00731612,0.02287389,0.01566402,0.01772195,0.00303468,-0.22577485,0.05687932,0.04155551,-0.03061534,-0.03282274,-0.050719,0.0026648,0.07086627,-0.02989583,0.00216638,-0.00124122,0.01118885,-0.03566492,-0.04074166,-0.02066951,-0.10028604,-0.03656409,-0.05289869,-0.01386527,0.08334772,-0.02860072,-0.00596212,0.00252024,0.0290531,0.02918674,-0.04246046,0.00177725,-0.01911382,-0.00540367,-0.0082638,-0.01010294,0.00066712,-0.08289002,-0.04959558,0.04579338,0.02566107,-0.04353236,0.06860381,-0.04274561,0.02215914,0.01455223,-0.01723673,-0.0234135,0.01330243,0.00274194,-0.06904019,-0.05901879,-0.02493079,-0.04107276,0.01839667,0.09753204,-0.03706396,-0.00380445,0.00605134,-0.01429463,-0.03509469,0.00239305,0.03328106,0.01336522,0.01637259,0.02419713,-0.0080438,0.05357055,-0.00799291,-0.00313418,0.00096596,0.02115868,0.04256241,0.04263521,-0.02019